snippet.title: INMOST - Release Date Trailer (Nintendo Switch & PC)
snippet.description:
Wishlist here: http://bit.ly/INMOST_Steam
Available from Friday August 21st on Nintendo Switch and PC!

Escape the depths of an otherworldly labyrinth in this cinematic puzzle platformer. Explore a hauntingly beautiful world, with three playable characters, in one dark, interconnected story...

Developed by Hidden Layer Games. Published by Chucklefish.
Music by Alexey Nechaev.

Steam: http://bit.ly/INMOST_Steam
Nintendo eShop: https://bit.ly/INMOST_SwitchNA
Humble: https://bit.ly/INMOST_Humble
GOG: https://bit.ly/INMOST_GOG

For more info on INMOST, follow the developers on Twitter!:
https://twitter.com/hlgteam
